The issue is that when I rotate the view for the first time, it works correctly, but when I rotate it from the other anchor, it jumps to another position. I believe this is because the rotation doesn&#39;t affect the position of the view. To fix this, I need to recalculate the new position of the view so that it moves accordingly, but I&#39;m not sure how to do that.

